Subject: rPSA-2008-0201-1 xorg-x11 xorg-x11-fonts
 xorg-x11-tools xorg-x11-xfs

rPath Security Advisory: 2008-0201-1
Published: 2008-06-21
Products:
    rPath Appliance Platform Linux Service 1
    rPath Linux 1

Rating: Severe
Exposure Level Classification:
    Local Root Deterministic Privilege Escalation
Updated Versions:
    xorg-x11=conary.rpath.com@rpl:1/6.8.2-30.14-1
    xorg-x11-fonts=conary.rpath.com@rpl:1/6.8.2-30.14-1
    xorg-x11-tools=conary.rpath.com@rpl:1/6.8.2-30.14-1
